{"tid":250401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 真三國無雙・斬(47) 屌雙兒兩Q, 賓周都損","createTime":"2017-05-20T04:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T05:55:19.000Z","uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0307ecfd7d9c0ab54aeb26f9593bc481d46941f","tid":250401,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>秒經必睇</strong></span></span><br />\n1. 升左lv先買成長禮包 拎唔拎得番之前個啲&amp;nbsp;<br />\n拎得番 可以一次過幾連10抽<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔啱屬既5-6星練唔練好<br />\n有愛可練 無愛可食<br />\n<br />\n3. 入坑前請三思 (不再補圖，因為冇人再敢抽)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0uqlw1s6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0uqlw1s6&h=21ab629b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uwnav1p8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuwnav1p8&h=6b35992d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 有用資料(轉巴哈)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=30635&amp;snA=635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D30635%26snA%3D635&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8f16f72c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=30635&amp;snA=635</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 修羅5-8擊破木桶成就<br />\n一開始係下面 唔好開自動行<br />\n<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">估計</span>只有三星通關先會掉武將<br />\n有試過唔係既巴打請糾正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>名將list及解說</strong></span></span><br />\n水:曹操 許褚 司馬懿 王元姬<br />\n木:諸葛亮 關羽 張飛 黃忠<br />\n火:呂布 孫策 大喬<br />\n<br />\n抽中岩屬=名將&amp;nbsp;<br />\n名將入手只可用元寶抽 (&lt;1%)<br />\n<br />\n抽中銀底<br />\n能力都會好過部份金底3/4*<br />\n不過好難升技 所以唔建議新手養<br />\n<br />\nbtw 602=呂布個女<br />\n(屌講左10尻幾次真係唔好再問，呢句生化吉兒講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>by中大貓奴</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>銀底名將數值係同4星金底將1樣<br />\n所以只計數值既話<br />\n金底名將&gt;銀底名將=金底4星將&gt;金底3星將</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">by波追人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>玉抽最勁可以抽到啱屬 3 星武將，例如周泰咁<br />\n滿技都好撚好打架。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">by問學人</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2b1fe98c912aa22ee6e5128dd4b0dedd9ca44d86","tid":250401,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Y61dd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Y61dd8.jpg&h=698f98ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIOS : <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1131126249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1131126249&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a35be0e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1131126249</a><br />\n<br />\nAN : <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nexon.dynastywarriors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nexon.dynastywarriors&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b251ea7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nexon.dynastywarriors</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A 睇左先好問</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1)  洗唔洗刷首抽 ?</span></span></strong><br />\n刷首抽game 唔刷就開局又唔課金會好辛苦   <br />\n<br />\n問: 如何刷首抽 : <br />\n答: AN機同IOS機都1樣 , 沒分別<br />\n先預備大量GMAIL (點樣大量申請自己諗啦 , 有電話認證限制)<br />\n做完教學記得去收信 , 會多幾抽<br />\n然後去 右上去設定 -&gt; 資訊 -&gt;綁定GMAIL-&gt;然後登出-&gt;再用遊客登入<br />\n(佢有個制係刪除帳號有冇用 ? 答你係無用既 , 一定要綁定登出先刷到) BY NEAR<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2)  點先可以開局 ?</span></span></strong><br />\n首先要知咩係啱屬 : 卡片背後會有顏色 , 金底即代表岩屬 , 能力值亦會係該角色中最高<br />\n自行參考下圖 , 紅框代表錯屬 , 黃框內代表岩屬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3crd56B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3crd56B.jpg&h=a105ac42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳國 火屬<br />\n魏國 水屬<br />\n蜀國 木屬<br />\n他國 火屬<br />\n另外亦有武將 唔啱屬都會勁過其他武將啱屬 如各名將 王元姬 呂玲綺<br />\n可參考 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7w250tJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7w250tJ.jpg&h=80eca171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(僅作數值比較 參考下好 技能 攻速等亦需考慮)<br />\n<br />\n不過除非你有極限耐性 , 否則唔好追5星6星好局<br />\n只要4星2-3隻啱屬性就可以開局 , 因為到最後都可以升上6星<br />\n只係前期會辛苦小小 當然搵D有得刷技就最好<br />\n包括 周泰 太史慈 董卓等<br />\n關卡掉落可參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2ae060ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3)  佢地話幫角色升技 , 係點升技</span></span></strong><br />\n答: 只要食番自己相同既角色就可以升技 , 例如呂布食呂布 (不過建議金底先好食其他) 升既技能點 = 肥料星數<br />\n金食金 金食銀 都可以 , 部份角色可以刷主線掉落<br />\n最好將肥料升到3星先食 比較慳錢 亦會+3技能等級 <br />\n<br />\n另外 用相同武將升星的話 會有額外技能點 <br />\n4星升5星 = 4+2 , 5星升6星 = 5+3 <br />\n升星時會以下一星級技能上限計數 即使滿左技都可以食左先<br />\n(5星武將技能上限10lv , 6星武將技能上限12lv)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4)  點樣由4星上5星 , 5星上6星</span></span></strong><br />\n答: 只要將要升星既角色升到滿等 , 食其他同星種角色(不需要1樣) , 被食角色不需滿等<br />\n4星上5星要4隻4星肥料 , 5星上6星要 5隻5星肥料<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5)  打到第幾關先會儲到3000元寶10抽 ?</span></span></strong><br />\n玩到你卡關都唔會有 一係等拎登入獎勵 一係課金 <br />\n(十連嘅話我係打到4-3 登入第4日會送元寶 咁就應該夠)BY 潛水會員<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6)  卡關點算   </span></span></strong><br />\n1. 搵好友手動打 試多幾次<br />\n2. 刷關升可以幫角色升星 , 升技 , 刷武器合成等等 , 打番前面既關卡 , 最好刷番你有既角色去升技<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">刷角及其他關卡資料，可以睇呢兩個(呢兩條LINK我未搵到邊個整，知道既話返我知THX)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1toDEosctYL06KypWso9PGYBlS2XX0jQSWw1nIA_g1JA/htmlview#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1toDEosctYL06KypWso9PGYBlS2XX0jQSWw1nIA_g1JA%2Fhtmlview%23&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7e8719d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1toDEosctYL06KypWso9PGYBlS2XX0jQSWw1nIA_g1JA/htmlview#</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">以上資料由巴打Near及及時行落巴打提供</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位巴打唔好再認錯孫權係呂布呀 ! 2隻好似樣</span>(BY Near)</strong>"},{"pid":"cbbaa708564ae975cf989e276f21deccc9260b54","tid":250401,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">裝備升級</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1rc3rd8hylRhK9bIXv8790ctIQuGeDtiEHJ1MlKtyaq8/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1rc3rd8hylRhK9bIXv8790ctIQuGeDtiEHJ1MlKtyaq8%2Fhtmlview&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d3886ffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1rc3rd8hylRhK9bIXv8790ctIQuGeDtiEHJ1MlKtyaq8/htmlview</a><br />\n<br />\n關於裝備滿等花費（按上面條link 做標準）：<br />\n<br />\n2星+20（3060 exp)（1件@$200）:<br />\n1:   11個1星 x $200=$2200<br />\n2:   5個1星+20（@$500）x$200 = $2900 <br />\n所以要2星滿等（+20）齋食1星就得。<br />\n<br />\n3星+20（4975 exp) (1件@400）<br />\n1: 4個2星+20（@$2200) x $400 = $10400<br />\n2: (8個2星 + 1個1星） x $400 = $3600<br />\n3: (4個3星 + 2個2星 + 1個1星）x $400 = $2800<br />\n<br />\n4星+20（7600 exp) (1件@800）<br />\n1: 13個2星 x $800 = $10400<br />\n2: (7個3星 + 1個2星) x $800 = $6400<br />\n3: 5個4星 x $800 = $4000<br />\n<br />\n5星+20 (24090 exp) (1件@1600)<br />\n1: (40個2星 + 1個1星) x $1600  = $65600<br />\n2: (24個3星 + 1個1星) x $1600 = $40000<br />\n3: (16個4星 + 1個1星) x $1600 = $27200<br />\n<br />\nps. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上面個表無6星所以無計，<br />\n但由此可見，食空等星既裝係會抵屌好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比各位巴打參考下，有錯請指出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>by生命裡那女孩</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d95f4089453f3f795787906669297f3ec35023f5","tid":250401,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"屌，柒左跟左上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38cec5b2db191e28d6b497ccc677a02b7d96f85","tid":250401,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b400c901ed50d6bdf0c3f82ac1121e0d7b701ff5","tid":250401,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，柒左跟左上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你跟住損埋啦咁"},{"pid":"a5fd3b53918a2d2c7ff38dd834c67329eb9fe648","tid":250401,"uid":20185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"爭d搶左1001 <br />\n好在！！"},{"pid":"a332303b70afb82131c79a6949ebdbca62f36819","tid":250401,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E7%9C%9F%E4%B8%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%99%E6%96%AC/520-%E7%AC%AC2%E6%B3%A2%E8%81%AF%E8%B3%BD%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95/1524685167576326/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259B%2599%25E6%2596%25AC%2F520-%25E7%25AC%25AC2%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%2F1524685167576326%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=657234f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E7%9C%9F%E4%B8%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%84%A1%E9%9B%99%E6%96%AC/520-%E7%AC%AC2%E6%B3%A2%E8%81%AF%E8%B3%BD%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95/1524685167576326/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二波武鬥場公告<br />\n屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be7e47df042b5c33073007b58134e73654bda46","tid":250401,"uid":57714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"642e0c36c085e794322186219bcbde0053a7cf25","tid":250401,"uid":57714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83c829b20fc69b87e080c5889c9902c6093f824c","tid":250401,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吹水台既屌 <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咪我</blockquote><br />\n係咪google play store cards送個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20蚊仲有冇 要大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnow 40 5抽十萬銀</blockquote><br />\n40不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽日有十抽</blockquote><br />\n大聲d <br />\nhow much?</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十抽連廿萬銀 75 聽日</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌心急開post 柒多鑊"},{"pid":"eacd7dd4c71067c7cf91e81f92e8baa8d749f99d","tid":250401,"uid":20185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吹水台既屌 <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n咪我</blockquote><br />\n係咪google play store cards送個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20蚊仲有冇 要大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnow 40 5抽十萬銀</blockquote><br />\n40不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽日有十抽</blockquote><br />\n大聲d <br />\nhow much?</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十抽連廿萬銀 75 聽日</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌心急開post 柒多鑊</blockquote><br />\n咩意思"},{"pid":"7800679d3c475c774145f181896c852ae56a03a8","tid":250401,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"大家去另一個po講啦"},{"pid":"31f8a4c35669c0d141fe1f22f7c0456e5bcc382a","tid":250401,"uid":20185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/250414/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/250414/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n去呢到講"},{"pid":"597bb18ab29b2626369f48b08e295c905c6cb4a7","tid":250401,"uid":94866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:55:19.000Z","msg":"原來你有開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}